data.description: Come check out this beautifully, remodeled farmhouse that awaits you in the City of Saranac!  This home provides plenty of natural lighting that has a mix of modern style but still the farm house charm!  The main level has a large mudroom as soon as you walk in the front door that provides abundant storage and updated cabinets and fixtures. The main floor also provides a laundry area, a large open-concept kitchen with an island, dining room, living room, full bathroom and an office or bedroom (no closet).  Upstairs you will find 3 bedrooms and a half bathroom. In the lower level there is a large layout for you to make it your own!  Outside you will find a brand new 3 stall garage. All new siding, a 3 seasons room, and a large fenced in yard! Schedule your showing today!
